---
---
<section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center text-center px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background glow effect -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[300px] h-[300px] md:w-[500px] md:h-[500px] bg-green-500/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] md:blur-[100px] -z-10"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl z-10">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-green-500/30 bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 text-sm font-medium mb-8 animate-fade-in">
      <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
        <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-400 opacity-75"></span>
        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-green-500"></span>
      </span>
      Automatización 24/7
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8 tracking-tight leading-tight animate-fade-in-up">
      Automatiza tu WhatsApp Business y <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-emerald-600">responde clientes 24/7</span> sin contratar personal
    </h1>

    <p class="text-gray-400 text-base md:text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-up delay-100">
      Ideal para negocios en Perú y Latinoamérica que reciben muchos mensajes y pierden ventas por no responder a tiempo.
      <br class="hidden md:block" />
      <span class="text-gray-300 font-medium mt-2 block">Ideal para: restaurantes, clínicas, tiendas online, servicios.</span>
    </p>

    <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-lg mb-8 animate-fade-in-up delay-100">
      Planes desde <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">$49/mes</span>
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center animate-fade-in-up delay-200 w-full sm:w-auto">
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/51941300176?text=Hola,%20quiero%20automatizar%20mi%20WhatsApp"
        class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-400 text-black font-bold px-6 py-3 md:px-8 md:py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(34,197,94,0.4)] hover:-translate-y-1 w-full sm:w-auto text-lg"
      >
        Habla con nosotros por WhatsApp
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
      
      <a href="#como-funciona" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors px-6 py-3 font-medium text-sm md:text-base">
        Ver cómo funciona
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 animate-fade-in-up delay-200 flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-green-500"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><path d="M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3"/></svg>
        <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">¿Es WhatsApp oficial? <strong class="text-white">Sí, usamos WhatsApp Business y reglas aprobadas.</strong></span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
        <span>🌎</span> Servicio disponible para Perú, México, Colombia y otros países de habla hispana.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  
  .animate-fade-in-up {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
  }
  
  .delay-100 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .delay-200 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
